Invocation Name: good deeds
des: Get ideas of what good deed you should do that day. Life is hard so its natural that we tend to focus on ourself and our own problems, but the reward that comes from helping others is priceless. Self-respect, confidence, and joy are just a few side effects of going out of your way to doing something nice for someone else, whether we think they deserve it or not.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
